  <brief_title>Cancer Venous Thromboembolism (VTE)</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase 3b, Prospective, Randomized, Open-label, Blind Evaluator (PROBE) Study Evaluating the Efficacy and Safety of (LMW) Heparin/Edoxaban Versus Dalteparin in Venous Thromboembolism Associated With Cancer</official_title>
